headline: Why HCA Healthcare (HCA) Shares Are Trading Lower Today
summary: Shares of hospital operator HCA Healthcare (NYSE:HCA) fell 3% in the morning session after the company's stock was downgraded by Bank of America Securities to 'Neutral' from 'Buy' due to concerns over recent legislation.
